Wizard Traiborn is a peculiar wizard who resides on the 1st floor[UK]2nd floor[US] of the Wizards' Tower. He often addresses people as "thingummywuts" and claims to see these indescribable creatures everywhere, claiming they cause minor havoc in the tower. Despite these seemingly mad theories and his goofy look, Traiborn is one of the Senior Wizards of the tower and possesses considerable magical skill. He is involved in the Recipe for Disaster, Demon Slayer, and Temple of the Eye quests.

Treasure Trails[edit | edit source]

Traiborn is the solution to the medium cipher clue: USBJCPSO. The answer to his challenge: How many air runes would I need to cast 630 wind waves? is: 3150.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • "Traiborn" rearranged spells "brain rot".
  • The bookcase in his room can be searched to find the following books that the player finds interesting:
    • 101 Ways to Impress your Mates with Magic
    • The Dark Arts of Magical Wands
    • Fire, Earth and Water - What's it all about?
    • How to become the Ultimate Wizard of the Universe
    • The Life & Times of a Thingummywut by Traiborn the Wizard
    • Living with a Wizard Husband - A housewife's Story
    • So you think you're a Mage? Volume 28
    • Wind Strike for Beginners
